It included that “there are great benefits in broadening the scope through which African American community life is viewed.  An image is a picture that triggers visual recognition and thus a relationship to (in this case, the newscast) product.  The implementation of creating new images that garner positive recognition of urban Americans will create a more, well-rounded, local and national audience in the face of  the new global economy and community.  As technology brings the world closer a clearer understanding of urban America is critical as they continue to grow economically, politically, and socially.
